        "text": "A bold, heavy solid black icon of a horizontal drum smoker. Front profile. One single, substantial contiguous dark mass of the cylindrical body, the domed lid, and the short, thick legs. High-contrast linocut style. Thick, bold white negative space is used only to define: 1) a chunky 'arc' handle on the lid, and 2) a single horizontal white 'slash' representing the heavy door latch. Rising from the lid are three thick, bold, geometric white 'S-curves' to represent smoke. No fine lines, no gray, heavy visual weight. Isolated on white. Optimized for a clean, single-boolean SVG silhouette.",
